title: Flight Simulator 2020 - How to - Fenix A320 -Configuring GSX integration
description:
In this video we will have a look at how to configure the GSX integration which has been added to the latest update of the Fenix A320. Using the integration you can benefit from the functionality GSX is providing while using the Fenix A320 as the aircraft.
